This is some content that I was playing with.
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th width="200">Criteria </th>
      <th>Good (5 points)</th>
      <th width="150">Fair (3)</th>
      <th width="150">Below average (1)</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Relevancy </td>
      <td>Photo matches selected category.</td>
      <td>Photo fits but might be better in another category.</td>
      <td>Photo does not fit category.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Technical Quality</td>
      <td>Photo is in focus, lighting and composition is good. </td>
      <td>Not in focus or lighting and composition could be improved. </td>
      <td>Not in focus and lighting along with composition needs improvement. </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Creativity</td>
      <td>Photo is unique, interesting and original. </td>
      <td>Photo is missing one crucial quality: unique, interesting and original.</td>
      <td>Photo is missing two or more crucial quality: unique, interesting and original.</td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td>Overall impression</td>
      <td>Photo holds the viewer’s attention and leaves and impression.</td>
      <td>Photo is notable, but does not match up to those judged Good. </td>
      <td>The photo does not grab the view’s attention.</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
